1
00:00:07,480 --> 00:00:08,410
Yao Shengsheng.

2
00:00:13,520 --> 00:00:16,180
Why did Stepmother come out of Qingzhou's room?

3
00:00:20,720 --> 00:00:21,650
Yao Shengsheng.

4
00:00:45,800 --> 00:00:46,560
Where am I?

5
00:00:50,360 --> 00:00:51,160
Shengsheng,

6
00:00:52,760 --> 00:00:53,880
why are you here?

7
00:00:54,120 --> 00:00:55,580
She was drugged by Yuemei.

8
00:00:55,760 --> 00:00:56,400
Brother,

9
00:00:57,120 --> 00:00:58,520
aren't you going to do something?

10
00:00:58,520 --> 00:00:59,980
I don't need you to tell me.

11
00:01:04,480 --> 00:01:05,880
She is the one I swore to protect.

12
00:01:05,880 --> 00:01:07,610
She is your sister-in-law now.

13
00:01:07,840 --> 00:01:09,080
Keep that in mind.

14
00:01:10,960 --> 00:01:11,560
Is that so?

15
00:01:12,920 --> 00:01:15,760
Then you didn't take good care of her on the wedding night,

16
00:01:15,760 --> 00:01:17,400
letting her end up like this.

17
00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:19,200
Song Qingzhou, I'm warning you.

18
00:01:19,640 --> 00:01:20,700
Stay away from her.

19
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:45,160
Thanks for saving me last night.

20
00:01:49,080 --> 00:01:49,940
It was nothing.

21
00:01:50,759 --> 00:01:52,360
But what will you do now?

22
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:54,600
Yuemei is going too far.

23
00:01:55,479 --> 00:01:57,140
You need to protect yourself.

24
00:01:58,160 --> 00:02:01,040
Speaking of which, I'm really curious,

25
00:02:01,680 --> 00:02:03,840
why does Yuemei have such deep feelings

26
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:05,320
for Song Huainan?

27
00:02:07,960 --> 00:02:09,720
Yuemei was my brother's maid.

28
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:12,680
She took care of him ever since she joined the Song family.

29
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:14,400
After spending so much time together,

30
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:15,800
she developed feelings for him

31
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:17,360
that she shouldn't have.

32
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:20,040
But my brother only saw her as a servant.

33
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:22,280
It was only after my mother passed away

34
00:02:22,280 --> 00:02:24,410
that my father took her as a concubine.

35
00:02:26,480 --> 00:02:29,340
There's something I've always been curious about.

36
00:02:29,760 --> 00:02:32,760
Song Huainan is your half-brother.

37
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:35,440
He outshines you in everything.

38
00:02:35,440 --> 00:02:38,360
You're always playing second fiddle to him.

39
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:40,260
Are you really okay with that?

40
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:42,440
Yao Shengsheng,

41
00:02:42,440 --> 00:02:44,970
this isn't something you should worry about.

42
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:47,040
Did I hit a nerve?

43
00:02:58,360 --> 00:03:00,400
Everyone pursues different things.

44
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:01,640
Money and power

45
00:03:01,880 --> 00:03:04,040
are indeed what many people dream of.

46
00:03:04,040 --> 00:03:07,240
But to me, they are just fleeting clouds.

47
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:09,640
They aren't what I want.

48
00:03:09,640 --> 00:03:10,840
Then what do you want?

49
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:16,970
I don't know either.

50
00:03:18,040 --> 00:03:19,000
But my brother,

51
00:03:20,200 --> 00:03:22,600
he really sacrificed a lot for this family.

52
00:03:23,079 --> 00:03:24,740
Everything in the Song family

53
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:26,370
rightfully belongs to him.

54
00:03:27,480 --> 00:03:29,440
Everything the Song family owns

55
00:03:29,720 --> 00:03:31,850
is stained with other people's blood.

56
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:49,260
Where did he put the jade pendant?

57
00:03:58,840 --> 00:03:59,400
Huainan.

58
00:04:01,600 --> 00:04:03,130
How did the negotiation go?

59
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:04,720
It went very smoothly.

60
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:14,040
Father, here's the situation.

61
00:04:14,480 --> 00:04:15,540
The foreigners...

62
00:04:18,760 --> 00:04:20,290
What are you talking about?

63
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:22,520
Father and I are talking business.

64
00:04:22,520 --> 00:04:23,520
You should leave.

65
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:25,600
Forget it. Let him listen.

66
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,720
He's old enough to make something of himself.

67
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:29,720
It's good to have some help later on.

68
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:32,720
Go on.

69
00:04:33,400 --> 00:04:35,800
Father, the foreigners' demands are clear.

70
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:37,960
As long as our soap factory starts production,

71
00:04:37,960 --> 00:04:39,200
for the next few years,

72
00:04:39,200 --> 00:04:41,000
they will sign huge orders,

73
00:04:41,280 --> 00:04:43,140
and capital will keep flowing in.

74
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:44,240
But right now,

75
00:04:46,440 --> 00:04:47,600
it's been so long,

76
00:04:47,880 --> 00:04:50,409
and we still haven't found the secret recipe.

77
00:04:50,520 --> 00:04:51,380
Secret recipe.

78
00:04:51,840 --> 00:04:53,560
Father, what secret recipe?

79
00:04:54,159 --> 00:04:54,960
It's nothing.

80
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:56,610
It's been resolved.

81
00:04:58,960 --> 00:04:59,720
Well done.

82
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:35,600
Father, it's almost time.

83
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:38,000
Those foreigners don't like people being late.

84
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:38,530
Let's go.

85
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:42,480
I'll see you out.

86
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:43,520
Okay.

87
00:06:22,960 --> 00:06:25,040
Secret recipe? What secret recipe?

88
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:27,320
I can't let Qingzhou catch him.

89
00:06:27,320 --> 00:06:28,480
The secret recipe and the Zhu family's affairs,

90
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:30,340
must absolutely be kept from him.

91
00:06:31,840 --> 00:06:33,840
It seems Song Qingzhou isn't allowed

92
00:06:33,840 --> 00:06:36,570
to participate in any major Song family matters.

93
00:06:36,840 --> 00:06:41,080
Does he know nothing about what happened to my family?

94
00:06:56,520 --> 00:06:57,240
What is it?

95
00:06:57,520 --> 00:06:58,360
Open it.

96
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:00,800
A gift for me?

97
00:07:02,440 --> 00:07:04,680
Isn't this the bracelet my brother gave me?

98
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:06,120
I promised to fix it for you.

99
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:07,520
Sorry it took so long.

100
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:10,400
Then I must keep it safe.

101
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:11,960
So if we argue in the future,

102
00:07:11,960 --> 00:07:14,290
you won't take it out on my bracelet again.

103
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:17,480
Well,

104
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:19,320
tomorrow afternoon, the Yao and Song families

105
00:07:19,320 --> 00:07:21,080
are having an unveiling ceremony.

106
00:07:21,080 --> 00:07:22,280
Why don't you join us?

107
00:07:54,440 --> 00:07:55,040
Industry.

108
00:07:56,720 --> 00:07:57,560
Industry.

109
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:06,160
Father-in-law, look.

110
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:08,860
I prepared this gift especially for you.

111
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:11,360
You are so thoughtful, Son-in-law.

112
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:15,460
The Yao and Song families are truly a perfect match.

113
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:18,200
Once this factory is up and running,

114
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:22,120
we will have no rivals in the whole country.

115
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:27,640
Let's commemorate this precious moment.

116
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:29,440
Come. This way, please. Good.

117
00:08:29,440 --> 00:08:30,560
Please, come.

118
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:31,360
Come on, everyone.

119
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:34,039
Let's squeeze in towards the center.

120
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:35,919
All right.

121
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:37,720
Smile, everyone.

122
00:08:37,720 --> 00:08:39,600
Three, two, one.

123
00:08:41,400 --> 00:08:43,159
Father, Mother.

124
00:08:44,240 --> 00:08:46,440
Remember the faces of these four people.

125
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:49,200
One day, I will use their blood

126
00:08:49,640 --> 00:08:51,900
to pay tribute to your spirits in heaven.

127
00:08:54,760 --> 00:08:56,480
Shengsheng, come here.

128
00:08:57,360 --> 00:09:00,020
You are the one to thank for this grand occasion.

129
00:09:02,360 --> 00:09:03,800
Okay, let's take another one.

130
00:09:03,800 --> 00:09:05,280
Look here. Don't blink.

131
00:09:05,280 --> 00:09:07,040
Three, two, one.

132
00:09:08,880 --> 00:09:09,800
Done. Thanks.

133
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:13,260
Huainan, I want to take a few more photos.

134
00:09:13,760 --> 00:09:14,320
Go ahead.

135
00:09:19,040 --> 00:09:20,160
Any new leads?

136
00:09:21,040 --> 00:09:22,560
I was just about to ask you.

137
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:29,170
Father-in-law.

138
00:09:29,720 --> 00:09:30,920
Help me find someone.

139
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:32,160
Who?

140
00:09:32,640 --> 00:09:34,500
Song Qingzhou's mother, I think.

141
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:35,960
I think she's different from the Song family.
